### [2 Chronicles Chapter 17](../../../bib/kjv/ch2017.htm#001.md)

[2 Chronicles](../../../bib/kjv/ch2001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">ch2 17:0</span></span>

Overview

[Ch2 17:1](../../../bib/kjv/ch2017.htm#001.md), Jehoshaphat, succeeding
Asa, reigns well, and prospers; [Ch2
17:7](../../../bib/kjv/ch2017.htm#007.md), He sends Levites with the
princes to teach Judah; [Ch2 17:10](../../../bib/kjv/ch2017.htm#010.md),
His enemies being terrified by God, some of them bring him presents and
tribute; [Ch2 17:12](../../../bib/kjv/ch2017.htm#012.md), His greatness,
captains, and armies.

